Place your SSL certificate files in this directory:

  cert.pem  - Your SSL certificate (or full chain)
  key.pem   - Your SSL private key

These files are referenced by the nginx configuration and are required
for HTTPS to work. They are excluded from version control for security.

For local development you can generate a self-signed certificate:

  openssl req -x509 -nodes -days 365 -newkey rsa:2048 \
    -keyout key.pem -out cert.pem \
    -subj "/CN=localhost"
